{
  "texts": [
    "First, it is necessary to judge how the practice of explanation in medicine reflects the criteria set out above.",
    "In line with the pragmatic turn, we have to pay attention to the particular context of explanations we find in medicine.",
    "We, in particular, set our sights on the doctor-patient relationship because we believe it may reflect some issues similar to those we encounter in xAI.",
    "Building on how doctors can explain their hypotheses to patients may provide a valuable blueprint for xAI.",
    "Second, we need to judge how capable the current AI is of following this standard and how its capability could be applied to medical xAI."
  ]
}